oard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=192.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> /bounce - raptor question</span><hr size=1> Ok so Saturday afternoon I was midway through 53, minding my own business sitting at the giant fort in BW casually ridding the land of giants and hornets and other pesky things that dared cross my path..<br>
<br>
Our guild's lone 60 wizzie needed me to help him with a transfer to his warrior twink.. afterwards he told me I should consider the raptors... at 53?  /shrug.  I hadn't been down there as of yet but figured from reading here that they were 54+ material with Pillar of Lightning as a minimum requirement.<br>
<br>
But he thought it was doable with Frost, so we went down there and he gave me a tour of the two islands and the different sets of raptors that could be pulled.  We decided after all was said and done I should stick to the small island.<br>
<br>
Well, it wasn't terribly long afterwards that I was 54, just going off the two southern statics + wanderer + VR on the small isle.<br>
<br>
After I got a bit more comfortable I worked in a 2nd kite of 3.. the two remaining statics on the north side, plus the single spawn on the north side of the big isle.<br>
<br>
15 game hours later.. I'm an Evoker.  =) =)  out of 54 almost as quick as I went into it.  Hence the /bounce!<br>
<br>
I do have a question though.  My wizard mentor said that 55 and 56 would &quot;fly&quot; by at these islands.. however I did a couple test kites.. same ones I was doing before.. and my bar moved less than it did in the 54 hell level thing (a quarter blue in 55 where I was getting a half blue in 54).<br>
<br>
Do I need to be on the big island now at 55 to keep seeing decent movement on the exp bar? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarmok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Armok</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(10/30/01 9:50:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=192.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: /bounce - raptor question</span><hr size=1> You can stay at small isle all the way to 58.  The main problem with small isle is that it is more often camped. Being able to break large isle just gives you more options and is more likely to ensure you a kiting spot.<br>
<br>
As for your levelling question:<br>
51-53 are hell levels<br>
54-58 are double hell levels<br>
59 is a triple hell level<br>
<br>
In addition to taking roughly double the experience of a normal level, each level from 54-58 takes a bit more than the one before.<br>
<br>
- Armok Komra &lt;Triton&gt;<br>
Sorcerer of Povar <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uapokkberzerk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Apokk Berzerk</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(10/30/01 11:00:54 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=192.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://142.55.42.238/apokk_head.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: /bounce - raptor question</span><hr size=1> I wouldn't do it at 53, sure IF you have decent mana gear you could pull it off with a bit of med kiting and harvesting, but lets face it, you are going to be utterly OOM after each kite...that's a full med cycle each time...ughhhh<br>
<br>
