</html></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utegellan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tegellan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(10/30/01 12:18:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=192.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: /bounce - raptor question</span><hr size=1>  The only advantage large isle holds over small is that it has 2 VRs, when you are in your later levels pulling them yields better exp, but getting it down so you can do it with no adds is tough to say the least.<br>
