<br>
I'll test it out some more later this week.<br>
<br>
Oh.. and I did quad 3 regs + 1 VR at 53 and had 20m left over.  No med kiting, no harvesting.  I seem to have less mana left from using PoL than I did using PoF.. and either way I have to finish the VR off with a draught at the end.  Still trying to figure that one out.<br>
<br>
I'm looking forward to the raptor guide that's being written.. see how the small isle strategy compares to the one that I developed after a while of being there. =)  And.. to see another interpretation of the big isle strategy.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uelupiousebonshire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elupious Ebonshire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(10/30/01 11:12:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=192.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.home.net/bwest92/Elupious.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: /bounce - raptor question</span><hr size=1> I did 4 regular raptors at 52-53.  Then I did 1 VR and 3 regulars at 54-55.  At 56-58 I started doing 2 VRs and 2 regulars.  I tried doing all 3 VRs at 57, but the added time to pull made it not really worth it.  It didnt really matter which island I was on until I needed to get 2 VRs, although small isle was a little easier to pull from since there was only 1 wanderer.  At 59 I got sick of the raptors and did Othmirs till 60, they gave about the same exp and had much better loot, I would recommend them starting at 57 if you have Pillar of Flame. <p><BR>
